headline: RTX to optimize cyber vulnerability detection for DARPA
summary: RTX's (NYSE: RTX) BBN Technologies was awarded a contract from DARPA to support its Intelligent Generation of Tools for Security, or INGOTS, program. INGOTS aims to strengthen cybersecurity by developing advanced methods to identify and mitigate complex exploit chains, preventing their use in real-world attacks.
